      {
        "unit_id": "U0002",
        "index": 2,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "星辉国际幼儿园——滨海市最顶尖的贵族幼儿园。铁艺大门，修剪整齐的草坪，教学楼的玻璃幕墙在阳光下闪闪发光。门口停满了豪车。",
        "scene_name": "星辉国际幼儿园门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 13,
        "line_end": 13,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "全景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0003",
        "index": 3,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌牵着予予站在幼儿园门口。其他家长穿着名牌、开着豪车，和她格格不入。",
        "scene_name": "星辉国际幼儿园门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 15,
        "line_end": 15,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "中景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0004",
        "index": 4,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "一个穿着高定风衣的妈妈牵着女儿走过来，瞥了沈念歌一眼。",
        "scene_name": "星辉国际幼儿园门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 17,
        "line_end": 17,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0005",
        "index": 5,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "风衣妈妈: 这个人怎么进的星辉？赞助费一年二十万，她穿得像刚从菜市场来的。",
        "scene_name": "星辉国际幼儿园门口·日",
        "speaker": "风衣妈妈",
        "line_start": 19,
        "line_end": 19,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "对旁边的闺蜜低声"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0006",
        "index": 6,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌听到了。她低头看了一眼自己的白T恤和帆布鞋——予予的手术费预付款已经掏空了所有积蓄，她连一件新衣服都买不起。",
        "scene_name": "星辉国际幼儿园门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 21,
        "line_end": 21,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0007",
        "index": 7,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "但她没有低头。她牵紧予予的手，走进了幼儿园。",
        "scene_name": "星辉国际幼儿园门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 23,
        "line_end": 23,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0008",
        "index": 8,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 妈咪，你在想什么？",
        "scene_name": "星辉国际幼儿园门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 25,
        "line_end": 25,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "仰头看她"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0009",
        "index": 9,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈念歌: 在想予予今天要好好表现。",
        "scene_name": "星辉国际幼儿园门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈念歌",
        "line_start": 27,
        "line_end": 27,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "笑了一下"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0010",
        "index": 10,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 放心吧！我最厉害了！",
        "scene_name": "星辉国际幼儿园门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 29,
        "line_end": 29,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "挺胸"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0011",
        "index": 11,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "scene",
        "text": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 35,
        "line_end": 35,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0012",
        "index": 12,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "教室宽敞明亮，彩色墙壁，每个孩子有自己的小柜子。十几个孩子和他们的家长坐成一圈，老师站在中间。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 37,
        "line_end": 37,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "中景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0013",
        "index": 13,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "老师: 今天是我们中班的第一天，请小朋友们轮流做自我介绍好不好？先说名字，再说一个关于自己的秘密。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "老师",
        "line_start": 39,
        "line_end": 39,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "笑着"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0014",
        "index": 14,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "孩子们一个个轮流。有的说喜欢吃草莓，有的说家里有游泳池，有的说暑假去了巴黎。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 41,
        "line_end": 41,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0015",
        "index": 15,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "轮到予予。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 43,
        "line_end": 43,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0016",
        "index": 16,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "他站起来，背带裤的背带松了一边，头发有点翘。但站得很直。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 45,
        "line_end": 45,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0017",
        "index": 17,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 大家好，我叫沈知予。小名予予。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 47,
        "line_end": 47,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "声音清脆"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0018",
        "index": 18,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "老师: 予予的秘密是什么呀？",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "老师",
        "line_start": 49,
        "line_end": 49,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0019",
        "index": 19,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 我爸爸是这个城市最厉害的人。但我还没见过他。等我找到他，他会变得很厉害。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 51,
        "line_end": 51,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "想了想，很认真地说"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0020",
        "index": 20,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "教室里安静了一秒。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 53,
        "line_end": 53,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0021",
        "index": 21,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "几个家长互相看了一眼，表情微妙。那个风衣妈妈小声笑了一下。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 55,
        "line_end": 55,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "近景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0022",
        "index": 22,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌坐在角落的家长席上，手指掐进了掌心。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 57,
        "line_end": 57,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0023",
        "index": 23,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "老师: 予予的爸爸一定很了不起。那你有没有什么爱好呢？",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "老师",
        "line_start": 59,
        "line_end": 59,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "愣了一下，随即温柔地"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0024",
        "index": 24,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 我喜欢画画。还有数学。100以内的加减法我都能算。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 61,
        "line_end": 61,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0025",
        "index": 25,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "老师: 真的吗？那老师考考你。37加58等于多少？",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "老师",
        "line_start": 63,
        "line_end": 63,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "惊讶"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0026",
        "index": 26,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "予予张口就来：",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 65,
        "line_end": 65,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0027",
        "index": 27,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 95。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 67,
        "line_end": 67,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0028",
        "index": 28,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "老师愣住了。旁边一个戴眼镜的小男孩掰着手指算了半天还没算出来。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 69,
        "line_end": 69,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0029",
        "index": 29,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "予予补了一句：",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 71,
        "line_end": 71,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0030",
        "index": 30,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 这个很简单呀。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 73,
        "line_end": 73,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "歪头，无害地笑了"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0031",
        "index": 31,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "教室里其他家长的表情变了。从之前的微讽变成了惊讶——甚至有人掏出手机看了一眼这个孩子的资料。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 75,
        "line_end": 75,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "中景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0032",
        "index": 32,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌看着儿子，嘴角弯了一下，但很快抿回去。她在心里叹了口气——予予太聪明了。聪明的孩子，容易被人记住。被人记住，就容易出事。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园教室·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 77,
        "line_end": 77,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0033",
        "index": 33,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "scene",
        "text": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 83,
        "line_end": 83,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0034",
        "index": 34,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "放学。家长们开着车来接孩子。豪车一辆接一辆驶过。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 85,
        "line_end": 85,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "全景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0035",
        "index": 35,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌站在路边，等公交车。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 87,
        "line_end": 87,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0036",
        "index": 36,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "予予背着小书包，从幼儿园里跑出来。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 89,
        "line_end": 89,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0037",
        "index": 37,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 妈咪！今天老师说我是全班最聪明的！还给我多发了一颗小星星！",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 91,
        "line_end": 91,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "兴奋地"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0038",
        "index": 38,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈念歌: 真棒。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "沈念歌",
        "line_start": 93,
        "line_end": 93,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "蹲下来帮他整理书包"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0039",
        "index": 39,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 妈咪，我告诉你一个秘密。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 95,
        "line_end": 95,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "压低声音，一脸神秘"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0040",
        "index": 40,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈念歌: 什么秘密？",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "沈念歌",
        "line_start": 97,
        "line_end": 97,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0041",
        "index": 41,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 我今天在幼儿园走廊上看到一张照片。挂在荣誉墙上。一个穿西装的男人，下面写着'陆氏集团总裁陆景琛先生捐赠'。妈咪——就是医院的那个叔叔！",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 99,
        "line_end": 99,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "左右看了看，凑到她耳边"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0042",
        "index": 42,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌的表情僵了一瞬。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 101,
        "line_end": 101,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "近景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0043",
        "index": 43,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈念歌: 嗯……可能是吧。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "沈念歌",
        "line_start": 103,
        "line_end": 103,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "声音尽量平稳"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0044",
        "index": 44,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 我就知道！他就住在这个城市！妈咪，你今天不是去他上班的地方了吗？你有没有看到他？",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 105,
        "line_end": 105,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "眼睛亮了"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0045",
        "index": 45,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "公交车来了。沈念歌站起来，牵起予予的手。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 107,
        "line_end": 107,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0046",
        "index": 46,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈念歌: 走了，公交车来了。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "沈念歌",
        "line_start": 109,
        "line_end": 109,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "岔开话题"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0047",
        "index": 47,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 妈咪，他既然捐赠了幼儿园，说明他是个好人。好人的话，应该不会不认自己的儿子吧？",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 111,
        "line_end": 111,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "被牵着上了车，还在回头看着幼儿园的方向"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0048",
        "index": 48,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌的背影在公交车台阶上顿了一下。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 113,
        "line_end": 113,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "特写",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0049",
        "index": 49,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "她没有回答。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 115,
        "line_end": 115,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0050",
        "index": 50,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "公交车关门，驶远了。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 117,
        "line_end": 117,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0051",
        "index": 51,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "幼儿园对面的一棵梧桐树下，一辆黑色轿车停在那里。车窗半降，赵一鸣坐在驾驶座，手里拿着一份幼儿园通讯录。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 119,
        "line_end": 119,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "中景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0052",
        "index": 52,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "手机响了。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 121,
        "line_end": 121,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0053",
        "index": 53,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "陆景琛: 查到了吗？",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "陆景琛",
        "line_start": 123,
        "line_end": 123,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "电话里"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0054",
        "index": 54,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "赵一鸣: 查到了。陆总，那个孩子……确实在星辉。今天第一天入园。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "赵一鸣",
        "line_start": 125,
        "line_end": 125,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0055",
        "index": 55,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "**电话那头沉默了片刻。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 127,
        "line_end": 127,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0056",
        "index": 56,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "陆景琛: 他今天说了什么？",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "陆景琛",
        "line_start": 129,
        "line_end": 129,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0057",
        "index": 57,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "赵一鸣: 他说……'我爸爸是这个城市最厉害的人。但还没见过他。'",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "赵一鸣",
        "line_start": 131,
        "line_end": 131,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "犹豫了一下"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0058",
        "index": 58,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "电话那头又是一阵沉默。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 133,
        "line_end": 133,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0059",
        "index": 59,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "陆景琛: ……知道了。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "陆景琛",
        "line_start": 135,
        "line_end": 135,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "声音很轻"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0060",
        "index": 60,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "电话挂断。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 137,
        "line_end": 137,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0061",
        "index": 61,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "赵一鸣看着手机屏幕，叹了口气。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 139,
        "line_end": 139,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0062",
        "index": 62,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "轿车后视镜里，公交车已经消失在路的尽头。",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 141,
        "line_end": 141,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "特写",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0063",
        "index": 63,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "music",
        "text": "音乐提示：吉他轻拨，一丝暖意中带着悬念",
        "scene_name": "幼儿园门口·傍晚",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 143,
        "line_end": 143,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
